title: Implement dynamic model caching and ensure we keep an up-to-date record of models available for each provider in the DB. We should seed this with our offline cached list if the table doesn't exist, and we can add new models. There's a `<baseurl>/models` route on the OpenAI API thing I think at least. xiaomi supports that at least.
